s=\"heading-style-h3\">Our clients trust us with their biggest decisions, from protecting their family interests to growing national businesses. Whatever your goals, <span class=\"yellow\">we help you achieve more</span>.</h2></div><div class=\"w-layout-grid statistics-grid_list\"><div id=\"w-node-_085dab50-7421-595c-17a5-fcdde4d3485d-e4d34857\" class=\"statistics-grid_item\"><p>Our 33 partners bring deep expertise across our services, so you always have senior input, clear direction, and decisions you can trust.</p><h3 class=\"text-style-statistic\">33</h3></div><div id=\"w-node-_085dab50-7421-595c-17a5-fcdde4d34862-e4d34857\" class=\"statistics-grid_item\"><p>240 people make up our team, each bringing their own perspective and drive to help you get the right result.</p><h3 class=\"text-style-statistic\">240</h3></div><div id=\"w-node-_085dab50-7421-595c-17a5-fcdde4d34867-e4d34857\" class=\"statistics-grid_item\"><p>Our 4.7 out of 5 rating on ReviewSolicitors, based on more than 3,500 reviews, reflects the trust, consistency, and care our clients experience every day.</p><h3 class=\"text-style-statistic\">4.7</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section fade=\"trigger\" id=\"w-node-_962b753c-4ddc-3450-0003-3e8660b5ceba-60b5ceba\" class=\"section_why-us\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"why-us_component\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xlarge\"><h2 data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h1\">Why work with us</h2></div><div class=\"w-layout-grid timeline4_content\"><div id=\"w-node-_209249c2-9afc-4ae2-0c65-d5f43b6a6285-60b5ceba\" class=\"timeline4_progress\"><div class=\"timeline4_fade-overlay-top\"></div><div class=\"timeline4_progress-line\"></div><div class=\"timeline4_line\"></div><div class=\"timeline4_fade-overlay-bottom\"></div><div fade=\"details\" class=\"timeline4_progress-line-cover\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_content-right\"><div fade=\"details\" class=\"timeline4_row\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle-wrapper\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_item\"><div class=\"max-width-small\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Clear advice. Real understanding.</h3></div><p>Legal support should feel personal, not transactional. We take the time to understand what you’re trying to achieve and what matters most to you. We speak plainly and explain your options clearly. We guide you through each stage so you always know where you stand and what comes next.</p></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_row\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle-wrapper\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_item\"><div class=\"max-width-small\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Expertise you can rely on.</h3></div><p>From everyday matters to complex challenges, our specialists bring deep experience across business, personal, and sector specific work. You’ll have expert support and practical solutions shaped around your situation. We think commercially, act decisively and tailor our advice to fit you. Never a one size fits all approach.</p></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_row\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle-wrapper\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_item\"><div class=\"max-width-small\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h3\">A proactive team on your side.</h3></div><p>We act quickly, think ahead and stay focused on the outcome. Whether you’re navigating change, resolving a dispute or planning for the future, we keep things moving with energy and purpose. You’ll get practical support, clear direction, and results you can feel confident in.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"why-us_image_component\"><div id=\"w-node-_962b753c-4ddc-3450-0003-3e8660b5ceda-60b5ceba\" class=\"why-us_image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11b6415523cfef1ca97fd_resized_1920_meeting3.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.1\" alt=\"Smiling woman with black hair typing on a laptop at a desk near a window.\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11b6415523cfef1ca97fd_resized_1920_meeting3-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11b6415523cfef1ca97fd_resized_1920_meeting3-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11b6415523cfef1ca97fd_resized_1920_meeting3-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11b6415523cfef1ca97fd_resized_1920_meeting3-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11b6415523cfef1ca97fd_resized_1920_meeting3.avif 1920w\" class=\"image is-parallax\"></div><div id=\"w-node-_962b753c-4ddc-3450-0003-3e8660b5cedc-60b5ceba\" class=\"why-us_image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11c376d4c3516aec10398_resized_1920_meeting5.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.1\" alt=\"Two men sitting at a table, smiling and looking at each other, with a laptop in front of them.\" class=\"image is-parallax\"></div></div></div></div></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></section><section data-wf--text-image--variant=\"left-aligned\" class=\"section_text\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"text-image_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid text-image_content\"><div class=\"text-image_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h2 data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Our team is our greatest strength</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Everyone in our team brings their own strengths and experience. What unites us is a shared commitment to delivering exceptional legal support through approachability, professionalism, and authenticity.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"b